And last Sunday evening, I preached a message about the Lord led me.

00:00:49.639 --> 00:00:51.439
And it's kind of interesting, I'll share a quick testimony.

00:00:51.439 --> 00:00:53.439
We were out doing some door hangers yesterday.

00:00:53.439 --> 00:00:56.040
