00:00:56.040 --> 00:00:57.919
door hangers out.

00:00:57.919 --> 00:01:00.500
And we had about 200 left that we needed to get distributed.

00:01:00.500 --> 00:01:05.559
So Joseph and I went over to an apartment complex, we're going to get it done.

00:01:05.559 --> 00:01:10.480
And we're going, and there's four flights, four levels to these apartment complexes,

00:01:10.480 --> 00:01:12.239
