00:01:12.239 --> 00:01:15.599
And he's on one building, I'm on another building, and we're doing it.

00:01:15.599 --> 00:01:19.879
And as I'm nearing the end, I'm kind of counting how many I have left, and I'm going up to

00:01:19.879 --> 00:01:21.339
the third level.

00:01:21.339 --> 00:01:24.120
And I knew that I was going to be too short for the fourth level.

00:01:24.120 --> 00:01:26.199
