00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:45.000
And so I get up to the third level, and not one door on the third level had doormats.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.519
Now I had enough for the third level, but I was a little bit, just being honest, I was

00:01:48.519 --> 00:01:52.519
a little bit like my faith was kind of, all right, I prayed that two on the fourth level

00:01:52.519 --> 00:01:55.919
